Product APIs
1. GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/product/
2. GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/product/<PRODUCT_ID>
3. POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/product/
Payload
{
    "name": "Product1",
    "price": 99.99,
    "description": "This is a sample product",
    "image_url": "http://example.com/product1.jpg"
}
4. PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/products/<PRODUCT_ID>
Payload
{
    "name": "Product1",
    "price": 99.99,
    "description": "This is a sample product",
    "image_url": "http://example.com/product1.jpg"
}
5. DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/product/<PRODUCT_ID>

